{"tid":1509153,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"以前都唔信真係有三毛半夜開工，睇到呢個泛民冚家剷嘅熱門po真係不得不信","createTime":"2019-08-26T17:41:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T17:58:13.000Z","uid":219269,"like":92,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"f7d731a06e0a0fbc68b5d7d511140059ff0c2a39","tid":1509153,"uid":219269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T17:41:44.000Z","msg":"[推上熱門] 我正式警告你班泛民冚家剷，如果你搞到《香港人權與民主法案》過唔撚到嘅話，你哋嘅下場會畀保皇黨更慘。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1509064\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1509064</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n入面樓主quote出嚟嘅嘢完全同標題無關<br />\n講到明係葉劉同鐘國賓<br />\n然後就改一個咁嘅標題黨<br />\n跟手成班好似喪屍咁嘅會員<br />\n響廿分鐘內衝曬入去<br />\n瞬間推到十二頁<br />\n個撚個都話要聲討歷史罪人<br />\n究竟發生咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n推到連尼住出嚟交代呢班咩人"},{"pid":"61f7ac24d45a6da144eac45f4bd06c8e4560a933","tid":1509153,"uid":33930,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T17:42:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hjf7rg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hjf7rg.gif&h=994c84f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrgexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=f307abca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrgexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=9a07fe66\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrgexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=6d0713a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"056a3abf8c218d9fadcfa9c887f9695e0865b9ef","tid":1509153,"uid":219269,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T17:42:44.000Z","msg":"［述職］涂謹申見完美國國會議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1508202\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1508202</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n呢度明明講得清清楚楚"},{"pid":"f75870e0e7d7bdae415e83a9d9c1aec69974026f","tid":1509153,"uid":219269,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T17:44:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新民黨主席葉劉淑儀及自由黨黨魁鍾國斌上周應美國國務院邀請，前往蒙大拿州參與《香港-美國立法機關交流團》，葉劉淑儀表示，參與會面的4名美國國會議員都表明，希望香港近日的風波，能由香港自己解決，不應有外國勢力及中央政府介入。<br />\n<br />\n鍾國斌說，與會的美議員甚至表明，如果香港事情有外國勢力介入，反而會「make a mess」，故希望能由香港自行解決。<br />\n<br />\n葉劉表示，得知美國國會將在9月復會後，審議《香港人權與民主法案》，若法案獲通過，有份參與及通過修訂逃犯條例草案的人士，將會被凍結在美國的資產，及不批准到美國的簽證，但她表明，有向與會議員解釋，港府已強調修例工作已完全停止，故沒有必要立例制裁香港。<br />\n<br />\n她又指，由於美國國會的立法程序不同，所有法案都是由議員提出，並要經過參眾兩院分別通過，更要經過聽證會過程，立法程序較複雜，故她不擔心有關法案會在短期內會通過。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢度就係三毛樓主嘅內文"},{"pid":"aec00a5bdfcc04898fb5336781d638e23ac2b4b9","tid":1509153,"uid":33783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T17:44:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"efd644284960758da5cee712aee0d024c6b80957","tid":1509153,"uid":242724,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T17:47:05.000Z","msg":"留意，一直講緊凌晨2:00就開工，第2日訓醒有用既POST 就冇曬，其他POST 就俾人帶風向"},{"pid":"b310d07cda9685a3a16b0940dc0fca121a791ee9","tid":1509153,"uid":285794,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T17:47:30.000Z","msg":"P牌仔幫唔到你推<br />\n<br />\n另一邊個post真係純分化<br />\n不過今時今日仲見到d咁低質既分化post<br />\n好令人失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4cc1b07be62d46209f0b242f62feeb4b7524192","tid":1509153,"uid":219269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T17:47:31.000Z","msg":"唔講仲以為你地唔撚識字<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T2HJx5m.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=htt